SUMMARY:Block 1: NeetCode Algorithms (Integration)
DESCRIPTION:[Phase: Integration | Week 5 | Day 1]\n\nMedium tier. TIMED - 20 min hard cap per problem.\n\nIf you don't solve it in 20 min\, stop\, read solution\, move on. This simulates interview pressure.\nTalk out loud throughout - this is interview simulation.\nFocus areas: graphs\, dynamic programming\, backtracking\, intervals.\n\nAfter solving\, ask: could I explain this solution clearly to an interviewer? If not\, practice the explanation.\n\nRULE: No AI. No autocomplete. No copilot.\nIf you reach for a tool\, that is the muscle atrophying. Stay with it.
END:VEVENT
