UID:378e844a-99dd-4d05-956b-31b9d1307334
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/London:20260423T143000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/London:20260423T160000
SUMMARY:Block 4: Mock Interview Simulation
DESCRIPTION:[Phase: Integration | Week 6 | Day 4]\n\nFull simulation. Set a timer.\n\nWeeks 1-2: Pick 1 medium NeetCode problem. 25 min. Talk out loud as if someone is watching. Then pick 1 easy system design question and talk through it for 15 min.\n\nWeeks 3-4: 1 medium problem (20 min cap) + 1 system design (20 min). Record yourself if possible. Watch it back.\n\nWeeks 5-6: Use Interviewing.io or Pramp for a real mock with a stranger. If unavailable\, full 45 min simulation: 5 min clarify\, 25 min code\, 15 min system design.\n\nAfter this block\, you are DONE for the day.\n16:00-18:00 is leisure. No code. No study.
END:VEVENT
